iana.security_considerations:
This media subtype consists of a ccc_list SDP attribute value. The ccc_list
SDP attribute is defined in section S.5.7.2 of 3GPP TS 26.114; SDP is
specified in RFC 8866.

The ccc_list attribute consists of a list of codecs and profile information.
As such, it contains no active or executable content.

The security considerations for SDP described in section 7 of 
RFC 8866, including those for privacy and 
integrity protection, also apply to this media type.
